  "texts": [
    "Beauty and comfort are the two most important factors in fashion clothing design.",
    "However, it is difficult to achieve both of these simultaneously due to physical constraints such as gravity, clothing fabrics, etc.",
    "For example, when designing a suit, designers add shoulder pads to widen the shoulders to make the body appear tall and straight.",
    "However, this limits the movement of the wearer, and prevents them from raising their arms comfortably.",
    "Fortunately, it is possible to overcome the constraints on the physical properties of materials in the Metaverse."
  ],
